<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>York Student Investment Fund</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      background: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: #1a1a1a; }

    .hero {
      padding: 5rem 2.5rem 4rem;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .hero-tag {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 3.5rem 2.5rem;
      border-top: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-grid p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    .stat {
      background: #f5f5f3;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .stat-num {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888;
    }

    .holdings {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .holding {
      background: #fff;
      border: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .holding-ticker {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .holding-name {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .holding-sector {
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
      background: #f5f5f3;
      color: #666;
    }

    .join-steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .step {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: #f5f5f3;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .step-num {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .step h3 {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .step p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .contact-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .contact-item {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .contact-item span {
      color: #1a1a1a;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      border-top: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    footer p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; }
      .nav-links { gap: 1.25rem; }
      .hero { padding: 3rem 1.25rem 2.5rem; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 28px; }
      .section { padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem; }
      .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .join-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .contact-row { gap: 1.5rem; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">YSIF</div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a>
      <a href="#join">Join us</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-tag">York Student Investment Fund</div>
    <h1></h1>
    <p>A student-run equity fund at the University of York. We research, debate, and invest in publicly listed companies - building real-world experience in financial analysis and portfolio management.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="about">
    <div class="section-label">About</div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <p>YSIF is a student-led investment fund based at the University of York. Our members develop their skills in fundamental equity research, valuation, and portfolio construction.</p>
      <p>We meet bi-weekly to pitch, debate, and vote on proposals. Every member plays an active role in the fund's strategy, from sector coverage to risk management, giving them experience that goes beyond the lecture theatre.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">10+</div><div class="stat-label">Active members</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">7</div><div class="stat-label">Holdings</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">2026</div><div class="stat-label">Founded</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="portfolio">
    <div class="section-label">Top Holdings</div>
    <div class="holdings">
      <div class="holding"><div class="holding-ticker">ENSG</div><div class="holding-name">Ensign Group</div><div class="holding-sector">Healthcare</div></div>
      <div class="holding"><div class="holding-ticker">GLEN</div><div class="holding-name">Glencore</div><div class="holding-sector">Materials</div></div>
      <div class="holding"><div class="holding-ticker">BRK.B</div><div class="holding-name">Berkshire Hathaway</div><div class="holding-sector">Financials</div></div>
      <div class="holding"><div class="holding-ticker">CRWD</div><div class="holding-name">CrowdStrike Holdings</div><div class="holding-sector">Technology</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="join">
    <div class="section-label">Join us</div>
    <div class="join-steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">Step 01</div>
        <h3>Apply</h3>
        <p>Fill out our short application form. No prior experience required.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">Step 02</div>
        <h3>Induction</h3>
        <p>Join our induction sessions where you'll learn how the fund operates and understand the ropes fast</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">Step 03</div>
        <h3>Pitch</h3>
        <p>Research a company and present your investment thesis to the fund. Get voted in and start contributing to the portfolio.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="section-label">Contact</div>
    <div class="contact-row">
      <div class="contact-item"><span>Email</span><br>yorkstudentinvestmentfund@gmail.com</div>
      <div class="contact-item"><span>Instagram</span><br>@ysif_york</div>
      <div class="contact-item"><span>LinkedIn</span><br>York Student Investment Fund</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 York Student Investment Fund</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>